# Background Service Worker Module

## PURPOSE
Background script that runs independently of UI.
Handles long-running tasks, message passing, and background operations.

## CONTAINS
- service-worker.js: Main background service worker

## RESPONSIBILITIES
- Listen for extension events (install, update)
- Handle message passing between UI and background
- Manage authentication state
- Coordinate background scans if needed
- Handle alarms and scheduled tasks
- Manage extension lifecycle

## REFERENCES
- Parent: /src/.windsurf
- Root: /.windsurf
- Communicates with: /src/ui/*, /src/core/*

## RULES
- Keep service worker lightweight
- Use message passing for UI communication
- Handle service worker lifecycle (can be terminated anytime)
- Store state in chrome.storage, not memory
- Minimize API calls from background
